          "Strict monotonicity of $\\arctan$ gives $\\dfrac{1}{n+1}>\\dfrac{1}{10}$, i.e. $n+1<10$, so $n\\le 8$; equality $\\frac{1}{n+1}=\\frac{1}{10}$ at $n=9$ corresponds to $S_9=T$ and is excluded.",
